+ Managing Secret\nScope Permissions
++ Permission levels
+++_ READ: retrieve values
+++_ WRITE: add/update (Databricks-backed only)
+++_ MANAGE: read + control permissions
++ CLI commands
+++_ put-acl: grant permission
+++_ list-acls: view all acls
+++_ get-acl: check specific principal
+++_ delete-acl: remove access
++ Key Vault-backed note
+++_ WRITE not applicable
+++_ Manage secrets in AKV directly
++ Premium plan requirement
+++_ Restricting MANAGE to creator only
@endmindmap
